'''Nomers Ocean''' was a body of [[Water/Legends|water]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Brosi]] in the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]]. [[Nihun River]] and [[West Reyno River]] flowed into it.<ref name="Alliance Intelligence Reports">''[[Alliance Intelligence Reports]]''</ref>

A part of Nomers Ocean was within the sphere of influence of the [[Brosin Underground]] around [[2 ABY/Legends|2 ABY]].<ref name="Alliance Intelligence Reports" />

